anastasiabeverlyhills Brow Freeze 🤍

The Anastasia Beverly Hills Brow Freeze works like there’s no time to waste. I mean, I’ve used clear or tinted eyebrow styling gels and mascaras except for soaps, but I read that even eyebrow soaps don’t set brow hairs as fast as this brow wax. This is a super quick-dry formula and I like it not only for that fact but also for the structure it gives by lifting and holding those eyebrow hairs in shape and place. There were reviews saying that it can last all day but personally, the Anastasia Beverly Hills Brow Freeze could only last me for about 3 to 4 hours at best. Into the 3rd hour my brow hairs started to go limp. The structure of it gave way, but at least my brows still look full and feathery with their shapes still intact.

Meninas, tudo bem? Hoje quero falar sobre o Delineador Labial Anastasia, que tem se tornado um item indispensável na minha rotina de maquiagem.

Com ele, consigo criar um contorno perfeito nos lábios, deixando-os mais definidos e volumosos. Além disso, sua textura cremosa facilita a aplicação e proporciona um acabamento impecável.

O Delineador Labial Anastasia também é extremamente duradouro, o que significa que não preciso me preocupar em retocar a maquiagem várias vezes durante o dia. Isso é perfeito para aqueles dias corridos em que não temos muito tempo para cuidar da maquiagem.

Se você ainda não experimentou o Delineador Labial Anastasia, eu super recomendo! Com certeza vai se tornar um dos seus queridinhos de maquiagem.

E aí, gostou dessa dica? Se sim, deixe aqui nos comentários sua opinião sobre o Delineador Labial Anastasia.

E se você já usou, conta pra mim como foi sua experiência! Ah, e não se esqueça de marcar suas amigas que também amam maquiagem e precisam conhecer esse produto incrível. 😉✨

☀️ ITS A MOTHER DAUGHTER THING 🌙

The dollhouse is officially expanding! I have graciously accepted an unbeatable offer to be apart of a long legacy of strong, powerful, ferocious drag queens like my fearless mother Alicia Boom Boom Chablis, my hardworking sister Bentley James, & my phenomenal grandmother Sydney Chablis who each set the example of what a professional, successful queen should be time and time again. I have such a respect and admiration for these charismatic gals as they excel where I may lack and I know I now have the opportunity to learn essential skills both on and off the stage from each of them. This may come as a surprise to some of you as our pairing can be seen as unique as pineapple on pizza but I assure you that we balance each other out wonderfully. Aria will always be a queen who rules through her own vernacular of kindness and love no matter her surroundings, the difference is now she has more of a backbone supporting her and a platform of visibility for the community. Don’t worry though Aria isn’t changing her name, her message, or her brand. This doll will always strive to bring the fun bubbly energy to every stage that she graces but she also now upholds a legacy that is so much bigger than her & personally I couldn’t be more excited to represent this fabulous house for everything that it stands for. At the end of the day I am proud to gain new friends and family while sharing the art of drag. I welcome all of my FIERCE fan club members to like & follow each of my drag family members as well as coming to see us at our monthly shows in Lansing at The Peoples Kitchen & Ellison Brewery. 💗

💋 𝐋𝐈𝐏 𝐁𝐋𝐔𝐒𝐇

Lip Blush is a cosmetic tattoo procedure, commonly known as a form of permanent makeup for your lips. 

This procedure is used to correct unevenness, neutralize dark lips, add colour to pale lips, define the vermillion border and/or add an illusion of fullness to the lips.

Wie oft wechselt ihr eure Pinsel? 

❣️alle 6- 12 Monate sollten aus Hygienischen Gründen die Pinsel ersetzt werden. 

❣️Reinigung, nach jedem Make up kann man die benutzten Pinsel mit einem Pinselreiniger und einem Tuch grob reinigen. Das ersetzt aber nicht bei Privatgebrauch die Wöchentliche und im professionellen Gebrauch tägliches Pinselbad. 

❣️Ich reinige meine Pinsel mit einem Shampoo und anschließend mit einem Conditioner. Das macht sie so unglaublich weich. (Puderpinsel)

❣️Bei flüssigen Kosmetika nehme ich einen günstigen dm_balea Gesichtsreiniger, eine Haselnussgroße Menge Reinigungsgel und reibe die Pinsel in meiner Handinnenfläche so lange- bis keine Farbreste mehr vorhanden sind. 

❣️Lasst zum trocknen die Pinsel entweder mit dem Applikationsbereich nach unten oder liegend trocknen. Dadurch kann sich keine Nässestau entwickeln. 

❣️und nun zu guter Letzt.... welche Pinselmarke verwende ich? 

Meine ersten Pinsel habe ich von meiner MUA Akademie pureidea.de gekriegt- danach hatte ich immer wieder die Pinsel von zoevacosmetics , maccosmeticsgermany , ysl dior und bhcosmeticsgermany .

Viel Spaß beim ausprobieren und schreibt mir doch in die Kommentare- wie und wie oft ihr eure Pinsel reinigt.
